{"tid":2258671,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"忽然諗起自己高中個數學老師","createTime":"2020-10-26T08:32:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T15:34:07.000Z","uid":300420,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"538046e172325b357ad9b7f8b714a782f2b72136","tid":2258671,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:32:06.000Z","msg":"巳經中學grad咗兩年<br />\n<br />\n仲記得佢話自己嘅夢想其實係做會計師 但係中學揀錯理科 大學又入唔到會計 <br />\n<br />\n結果讀完書之後就喺啲細公司做份閪工 又成日俾人恰 兜兜轉傳最後做咗老師 <br />\n<br />\n雖然過咗咁多年佢都係想做會計 但係已經冇機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰陣時見佢講到咁sad仲喺度笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點估到而家自己都驚有一日會變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af666280ecb736e02aab999e49c7fc3c3cffd3b","tid":2258671,"uid":4574,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:39:30.000Z","msg":"人生逆轉贏家<br />\n<br />\n拎到教席 立於不敗之地"},{"pid":"6c9cb0469a058f595a0d089208811dfd41c8b120","tid":2258671,"uid":300420,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"5af666280ecb736e02aab999e49c7fc3c3cffd3b","tid":2258671,"uid":4574,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:39:30.000Z","msg":"人生逆轉贏家<br />\n<br />\n拎到教席 立於不敗之地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:42:53.000Z","msg":"可以喺嗰個年代出世 其實做咩都係贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過喺香港黃金年代做會計好似贏得仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098b5198b2ff61332bb9b7b7696e727293b5138c","tid":2258671,"uid":66324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T09:54:18.000Z","msg":"做會計師會爆肝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd71858fbaad1b83eeb820d117a93003ecc2412","tid":2258671,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":